<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Advanced Placement: Transfer credit will be awarded for Advanced Placement scores of 3, 4, and 5. College courses taught in a high school under the sponsorship of an accredited college in which a grade of &quot;C or better&quot; is received, will receive transfer credit for those courses applicable to his or her program as determined by the dean responsible for the subject of the course.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.paulsmiths.edu/programs/advanced_studies/faq.php" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
